Nearby, a small fireplace crackles warmly, its glow casting a comforting light that contrasts with the chilly surroundings. Adjacent to the fireplace stands a charming coffee bar, complete with a coffee machine, ceramic mugs, and a vase of fresh flowers adding a touch of vibrancy. (Lyrics):
[Verse 1]
Two Augusts ago

I push my luck, it shows
